{"tid":2087551,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【香港獨立】沒有恐懼 只有憤怒","createTime":"2020-06-30T17:09:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T17:44:20.000Z","uid":53610,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b08bf4a42fcdbc4519a04799d897934fedb8b36e","tid":2087551,"uid":53610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T17:09:14.000Z","msg":"國安法出咗<br />\n冇感覺到一絲一毫的恐懼，只係覺得好笑<br />\n<br />\n驚？當你做咩都可能犯法仲有咩好驚？<br />\n<br />\n諗返過去一年發生的事，有手足流血受傷，甚至犧牲生命，有手足被判刑，前途盡毀，我哋打過國際線，都打過街頭戰，做過和理，都做過勇武，一次次的打壓，愈嚟愈深的黑暗，從來冇打敗過我哋，而我哋變得愈嚟愈強大<br />\n<br />\n無止境的打壓或者會令人卻步，但係我哋的憤怒遠超於恐懼，而恐懼亦無法挫敗我哋的信念<br />\n<br />\n就算係講笑，我都唔會向支那惡法屈服哪怕一絲一毫<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港獨立，唯一出路</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我打從心底睇唔起依條支安法，完全冇覺得驚的感覺，睇下支那幾時拉撚咗我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oiQGM5g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoiQGM5g.jpg&h=8bf0e591&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KeLC4RX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKeLC4RX.jpg&h=895f37d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3LpPVYC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3LpPVYC.jpg&h=3423651b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FdTtr5i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFdTtr5i.jpg&h=0ab793fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/30jTDbZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F30jTDbZ.jpg&h=ae50f3a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GiHmM5j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGiHmM5j.jpg&h=1b4a9690&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a9V7HDF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa9V7HDF.jpg&h=f7764206&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n